== About Me

As a researcher at Samsung, my work is focussed towards the [https://iwslt.org/2021/simultaneous simultaneous speech translation] task. \n
If you are interested to know more about my work, you can have a look at the initial parts of my recent publications. \n
Feel free to [contact.html contact] me for any queries/discussions.

